text.text: We ordered the sauerkraut BBQ fish, grilled scallops, grilled squid, grilled non-spicy wings, and noodles with onion oil. For the fish, we added on extra crispy and tofu at an additional cost. The sauerkraut flavor was quite mild ‚Äî we were expecting a bit more punch. The other dishes were alright; nothing particularly stood out, but they were decent overall.
